Description:
REAR ACCESS - PERFECT FAMILY HOME!
When you walk into this light home, you feel right at ease. This home boasts 3 good sized bedrooms with the master having a lovely bay window, walk in robe and ensuite. The master also has a ceiling fan to cool you down on those hot summer nights. The other two rooms both have built in wardrobes.
The family living and dining area consists of a split system cooler and ceiling fans as well, with newly laid floating floor boards. The kitchen is tiled with gas cook top and electric wall oven offering ample bench and cupboard space.
Outside has a huge under cover concreted pergola area leading from the back of the garage, which has rear roller door access perfect for access for cars, boats or caravans. There is still a sizable yard for the kids and animals to play on the grass!
Extras include:
- ducted heating,
- double remote garage with internal access,
- garden shed and so much more.
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.

Address: 38 Flash Dan Drive Cranbourne East VIC 3977
Description:
EXCELLENT ENTERTAINER!
CRANBOURNE EAST: Situated in the exclusive Cascades on Clyde Estate on a massive 528m2 block sits this immaculate family home which resides in prime position to public transport, parks, shops and schools.
The open floor plan itself offers four spacious robed bedrooms, the generous sized master complete with walk in robe and a full ensuite.
The kitchen which overlooks the huge front living area and separate dining comes complete with a 5-burner cook top, 900mm range hood, tiled splash back, stainless steel appliances and plenty of bench space with an abundance of overhead storage!
Added features include: ducted heating & evaporative cooling, down lights throughout, internal access, neutral tones throughout, multiple living zones and much more!
If you love huge outdoor entertaining areas then this wont disappoint, step outside to your quality built alfresco, this provides the perfect place to enjoy some much needed rest and relaxation after a long working week, while still having enough space to enjoy the convenient blend of grass and decking so kids can still have enough room to run around play.
The additions dont stop there, as you drive along this quiet, nestled away street, youll appreciate the enormous street appeal this home has to offer, with a completely landscaped front yard and an exposed aggregate drive way to your double lock up garage, youll be able to appreciate the amount of effort that has gone into the making of this perfect family home.
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

Description:
Fit The Whole Family!
Less than 2 years old, this contemporary 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, family home is ready and waiting. Conveniently located near Cranbourne East Primary School, Cranbourne East Secondary College, St Peters College, St Thomas Primary School, Casey Fields and within close proximity of Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, Cranbourne Recreation Reserve and Cranbourne Royal Botanic Gardens, this fantastic opportunity is not to be missed.

Positioned with easy access to both the South Gippsland Highway and the Monash Freeway, located close to several schools and lots of outdoor recreation space and sporting facilities, this fantastic residence is the perfect opportunity for the first home owner, growing family or astute investor. Call us today and snap up this wonderful home.

Description:
SOLD BY BRANDON WHITTA!
Cranbourne East: Located in the picturesque Cascades on Clyde estate sits this astonishing four bedrooms plus study delight, situated on a massive 612m2 block!
With an array of separate living zones, huge outdoor entertaining area with alfresco this exquisite residence is sure to suit even the pickiest of buyers.
The generous sized master bedroom comes complete with full esuite and walk in robes, while the three guest bedrooms come fitted with built in robes of their own.
With an open study that is large enough to be used as a formal dining or lounge area plus the added convenience of a huge rumpus, separate dining and main living zone. This home is sure to accommodate even the largest of families.
The kitchen which comes complete with stainless steel appliances, 900mm range hood, 5 burner gas cook top, tiled splash back, ample amounts of bench space and overhead storage, not to mention a functional amount of pantry space, all overlooking the alfresco and central living zone.
Added features include: internal access, down lights throughout, evaporative cooling & ducted heating, neutral tones throughout, two separate garden sheds and a fully decked alfresco area.
Step outside to your quality built alfresco, this provides the perfect place to enjoy some much needed rest and relaxation after a long working week, while still having enough space to enjoy the convenient blend of backyard and decking so kids can still have enough room to run around play.
The additions don?t stop there, as you drive along this quiet, nestled away street, you?ll appreciate the enormous street appeal this home has to offer, with a completely landscaped front yard and an exposed aggregate drive way to your double lock up garage, you?ll be able to appreciate the amount of effort that has gone into the making of this perfect family home.
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.

Description:
SOLD BY KATE RUSHTON
CRANBOURNE EAST ? LIVINGSTON ESTATE: You can?t help but feel at home once you step through this beautiful welcoming home. Positioned in the popular Livingston Estate with neatly presented homes and across the road from a park, this home will suit any family, first home buyer or someone downsizing.
Offering a functional floor plan with a wide entrance leading you to the master bedroom with walk-in robe, full ensuite and a separate toilet. Both other bedrooms have built in robes.
The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances - 900mm gas stove cooking, electric oven, range hood, dishwasher. Caesar stone bench tops with an island bench overlooking the family/meals area. The kitchen has ample storage with overhead cupboards.
Outside you have established fruit trees and a decked pergola area for year round enjoyment. The blend of indoor outdoor living is the feature of this home with light and bright living areas.
Extra features include:
- Split ducted refrigerated cooling
- Ducted heating
- Laminate floorboards
- Day and night shades throughout the home
- Quality light fittings
- Colour bond fencing
- Remote lock up double garage with internal access
- Carpeted bedrooms
The location of this quality home is second to none with the park on your door step your family can enjoy the open space for many years to come.
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.

Description:
**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
HUNT CLUB ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST (124238122): Only app. 5 years young this home, positioned in one of the area's most popular estates, amasses to around 26 squares under roofline and is built by impressive builders Boutique Homes. Presented in 'as new' condition 10 Challenger Circuit allows the lucky new purchaser to literally move in, unpack and relax!
Nestled on an easy to maintain, private corner block of app. 524m2 the property is fronted by a modern facade with rendered features that provide instant street appeal.
Inside, great natural light, light paint tones and floating timber flooring enhance the central hallway and open up the family/meals area which is complemented by a separate lounge or theatre room. The kitchen will please any keen chef with 40mm stone bench tops and a full complement of Blanco stainless appliances including a 900mm freestanding oven/stove.
There is plenty of accommodation for a large family with 4 robed bedrooms, including the master with a walk in wardrobe and a lovely ensuite. In addition you will find a pristine family bathroom, a dedicated study, ducted reverse cycle heating and refrigerated cooling plus an alarm for added peace of mind.
Outside you will be greeted by a double remote garage with internal access and a perfectly sized backyard complete with an alfresco entertaining area and a handy garden shed.
Within close proximity to picturesque wetlands and walking/bike paths the Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering a complete range of education facilities including a childcare centre, Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College. Buses weave through the estate whilst the recently opened Hunt Club Village has an array of shopping options. There are future plans for a Cranbourne East railway station as well. High speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs add to the overall appeal of this family orientated location!
The position is second to none! Centrally located to freeways and public transport enroute to the Melbourne CBD which is only app. 40 minutes away. For those of you who like to stay closer to home it?s only a brisk drive to Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, Berwick Village, Fountain Gate Shopping Centre, Casey Lifestyle Centre and Casey Fields Sporting Complex. Within close vicinity to an array of further Primary, Secondary and Tertiary Institutions, the entire family has easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation!
